language Essence 1.3

given n, k, numColours : int(1..)
given edges : set of set (size 2) of int(1..n)

find colouring : function (total) int(1..n) --> mset (size k, maxOccur 1) of int(1..numColours)

such that
    forAll edge in edges .
        forAll u in edge . forAll v in edge . u < v ->
            (forAll c : int(1..numColours) . !(c in colouring(u) /\ c in colouring(v)))
